The paper discusses the interaction between AI systems and humans, specifically in the context of plan explanations. This falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the need for the AI system to suggest changes to the human's model, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also presents algorithms for automatically computing these explanations, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the algorithms, which involves robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY).
